# Ignore everything by default in this test-data folder
*

# Allow the specific project directories & GitHub workflows
!.github/
!**/.github/**
!arogya_ai_backend/
!arogya_ai_backend/**
!arogya_ai_flutter/
!arogya_ai_flutter/**
!arogya_ai_web/
!arogya_ai_web/**

# Allow .gitignore itself
!.gitignore

# Exclude large binaries, logs, secrets, and build outputs
**/node_modules/
**/*.apk
**/*.aab
**/*.log
**/*_log.txt
**/*error.txt
**/build/
**/build_old*/
**/build_old**/
**/.gradle/
**/intermediates/
**/.dart_tool/
**/.idea/
**/.env
**/local.properties
